{"title":"数字对","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":250,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-3313","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p> </p>\n<p>对于一个数字对(a, b)，我们可以通过一次操作将其变为新数字对(a+b, b)或(a, a+b)。</p>\n<p>给定一正整数n，问最少需要多少次操作可将数字对(1, 1)变为一个数字对，该数字对至少有一个数字为n。</p>\n<p> </p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个正整数 n</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数表示答案。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>3</p>\n<p>【样例解释】</p>\n<p>(1,1)  →  (1,2)  →  (3,2)  →  (5,2)</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p> 对于30%的数据， 1 &lt;= n &lt;= 1000</p>\n<p> 对于60%的数据， 1 &lt;= n &lt;= 20000</p>\n<p>对于100%的数据，1 &lt;= n &lt;= 10^6</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}